sentence:
…Consultation.--In developing the report required under       subsection (a), the Comptroller General may consult with--

(1) the maritime and aviation industries;

(2) Federal Government agencies familiar with the use and       deployment of unmanned systems; and

(3) any relevant--

(A) federally funded research institutions;

(B) nongovernmental organizations;…

…or in use at 1 or more       agencies to--

(A) increase the interoperability of software licenses,       including software entitlements and software built by       Government agencies;

(B) consolidate licenses, as appropriate;

(C) reduce costs;

(D) improve performance; and

(E) modernize the management and oversight of software       entitlements…
